ManiShop
========

 * cosmoliva.com - check out the products
 * change currency
 * set product amount on /store/cart/


Long Term Goals
===============

 * Split apps of the project and make em more generic for individual usage.
 * Search.
 * Credit card support.
 * Paypal support.
 * SMS updates of new (approved) checkouts.
 * Newsletter.
 * Wishlist.
 * RSS feed of new products added.
 * Customer section.
 * Registered users, should be able to:
 	comment on a product,
 	rate a product,
	mark a product as insultive.
